data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER BRING US A OFFER ON THIS, SPACIOUS OPEN FLOOR PLAN,WITH A HUGE GREAT ROOM THAT OPENS UP INTO THE DINING ROOM AND KITCHEN. ALL NEW PAINT, CARPET, WATER PROOF LAMINATE, CERAMIC IN THE KITCHEN, NEW GARBAGE DISPOSAL, DON'T FORGET THE BRAND NEW 6 FT PRIVACY FENCE IN THE HUGE BACK YARD. NEWER ROOF AND AC UNIT. TO MUCH TO LIST. THE GARAGE IS 2 CAR AND FINISHED DRYWALL AND HAS A BRAND NEW GARAGE DOOR. THE COMMUNITY HAS A COVERED SHELTER FOR PICNICS /PLAY GROUND AREA , A SPLASH PARK, POOL, AND A BEAUTIFUL POND TO SET WHILE ENJOYING THE WILD LIFE. PLUS A COMMUNITY CLUB HOUSE. THIS HOME IS IN MOVE IN CONDITION. REFRIGERATOR,  STOVE, DISHWASHER ALL STAY WITH THE HOME.
